kquote><br />\n方法1 正路，但值得一提係本身permanent 轉你做freelance 勞法上就要一個月通知期或補一個月錢，而推薦信就無包嘅，why not both?"},{"pid":"370cd50bd907e336983cf3fb395b04168c5c7856","tid":295413,"uid":16270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T18:02:05.000Z","msg":"生果報？"},{"pid":"f0dabf5aa730a280153997100e12d5f2826796e9","tid":295413,"uid":43806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T18:02:25.000Z","msg":"你做左5個月先岩岩過試用 <br />\n你個試用期有冇咁長呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a1445a2494ee8fabc3b6c8efb257729a1901770","tid":295413,"uid":44486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T18:03:42.000Z","msg":"轉工"},{"pid":"ae4f58e64c8f3d79d594dd41dadb50f26d5b6db6","tid":295413,"uid":82310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T18:54:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>照做住搵工<br />\n1. 轉約應該當完約公司補一個月，同公司deal唔使補，但比返封推薦信你<br />\nor 2. 同新公司講去旅行短期課程散工咩都好，當呢份冇存在過</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 方法1好似幾好</blockquote><br />\n方法1 正路，但值得一提係本身permanent 轉你做freelance 勞法上就要一個月通知期或補一個月錢，而推薦信就無包嘅，why not both?</blockquote><br />\n樓主開得個咁既po，怕且冇ref. letter應該怕過擇咗佢春袋，<br />\n而公司補得一個月分分鐘就唔出ref letter<br />\n冇錯，我都認呢個做法好重性奴"},{"pid":"2df70f7ac3941bdde6235690ed68691069803001","tid":295413,"uid":109650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T14:35:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"69109618a49e59ce204d2ebfc136bbd37da3c10e","tid":295413,"uid":11285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T14:53:32.000Z","msg":"當白紙搵過算鳩數啦"},{"pid":"f9599b705c08bb3b782aac3b84c5f151e21fe303","tid":295413,"uid":109650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T15:27:17.000Z","msg":"<blockq